Ronald's Xmonad configuration

This configuration is used in Xmonad .9 on Archlinux

* Installation ( http://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Xmonad )

    # packer -S xmonad-darcs xmonad-contrib-darcs

* Starting xmonad from ~/.xinitc

    $ xsetroot -cursor_name left_ptr
    $ feh --bg-scale /home/ronald/bin/tinypilot.jpg &
    $ exec ck-launch-session xmonad
